}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== From one GS608v3... *The Switch IC is covered by a massive heatsink on this unit (~3.5 times the width of the chip). **Unk. chipset vendor, large LQFP package *No visible '''DNI''' part code / number / whatever is visible (it may be under the heatsink covered region), but a seemingly typical '''DNI''' label is affixed to the back of the unit - they're still presumed to be the manufacturer *A date code of '''0929''' is silkscreened on the board
